      <Value Culture="en-US"><![CDATA[{
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b0c51460-6d98-44e8-8b81-22c4d2839082",
      "key": "afba31d7-932e-4857-92b5-9c2610ddb037",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Products"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Container <em>solutions</em>."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">For energy providers and large systems</span></p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "backgroundColor",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            "Navy"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b0c51460-6d98-44e8-8b81-22c4d2839082",
      "key": "11100b16-7930-4503-a579-a89dac81f1b2",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Luminary-3790 <em>High performance</em>."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Designed for </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">large industrial and infrastructure applications</span></strong><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">With a capacity ranging from 1805 kWh to 3790 kWh and a C-rate up to 1C, the system is suitable for applications that </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">require fast response and frequent charge and discharge cycles</span></strong><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">It features high power density, </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">scalability, and a service life of over 9.000 cycles</span></strong><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">.</span><br><br></p><ul><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Capacity 1805 – 3790 kWh</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">C-rate ≤ 1C</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">CATL battery cells 285 Ah / 3.2 V</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Liquid cooling</span></strong></p></li></ul><p><a data-router-slot=\"disabled\" href=\"#\" title=\"Skini specifikacije\" data-anchor=\"#\" type=\"external\">Download specifications</a></p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "image",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "f0755a95-4062-48d6-9df4-1de4d7c15f81",
              "mediaKey": "c13c8331-7317-4529-844d-15d189f41741",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b0c51460-6d98-44e8-8b81-22c4d2839082",
      "key": "aa00a66b-9998-4d3e-98f8-00c9fe4263c9",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Luminary-4070 <em>Longevity</em>."
        },
        {
          "alias": "text",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "<p><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">Designed for </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">long-term energy solutions in large-scale projects.</span></strong><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">With a capacity from 2035 kWh to 4070 kWh and an optimized C-rate ≤ 0,5C, </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">it provides a balance between capacity and longevity.</span></strong><br><br><span style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;\">It is designed for applications that require </span><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">high energy density and an extended service life, with over 10.000 cycles.</span></strong><br><br></p><ul><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Capacity 2035 to 4070 kWh</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">C-rate ≤ 0,5C</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">CATL battery cells 306 Ah / 3.2 V</span></strong></p></li><li><p><strong><span style=\"font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Liquid cooling</span></strong></p></li></ul><p><a data-router-slot=\"disabled\" data-anchor=\"#\" href=\"#\" title=\"Skini specifikacije\" type=\"external\">Download specifications</a></p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "image",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "f0755a95-4062-48d6-9df4-1de4d7c15f81",
              "mediaKey": "c13c8331-7317-4529-844d-15d189f41741",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
